description "Gran Mercenary

^2Weapons:
- Heavy Melee
- DL-44 Blaster Pistol (2)
- Thermal Detonator (5)

^8Attributes:
- Melee Resistance
- Strength (1)
- Heal (3)

^3Abilities:
- 3 Poison Darts ^3[CS1 Melee]
- Dodge (3) ^3[CS2]
- Gun Kick ^3[CS3]

This Gran mercenary serves as the group's demolitionist.  Once his thermal detonators are expended he serves as an excellent brawler."